%91%D9%81%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to spend zeal, pains and costs, to be eager (on a thing)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or fall in love, to like (بِ (bi) something), to be very attached (بِ (bi) to)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to get melasmata, to get irregular brown-reddish spots (of the face)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to entrust ([transitive] someone [transitive or بِ (bi)] with something), to impose (a matter on someone)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to assign (someone a task)","tags":["ditransitive"],"examples":[{"text":"لَا يُكَلِّفُ ٱللّٰهُ نَفْسًا إِلَّا وُسْعَهَا","english":"Allah burdens not a person beyond his scope."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to molest, to make difficulties for, to trouble"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cost (someone something)","tags":["ditransitive"],"examples":[{"text":"هٰذَا سَيُكَلِّفُكَ كَثِيرًا","english":"It will cost you a lot."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of كَلِفَ (kalifa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pains and care taken"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"amorousness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"melasmata, pathologically melanized skin portions","examples":[{"text":"بان شجرة معروفة لها ثمرة حبّها أكبر من الحمص مائل إلى البياض طيب الرائحة وله لبّ دهني قال الشيخ الرئيس إنه ينفع من البرص والكلف والبهق وآثار القروح وينفع من الثآليل أيضا في المراهم وطبخه ينفع من وجع الأسنان مضمضة وقال غيره ينفع من الجرب ويقطع الرعاف.","english":"The ben is a well-known tree with a fruit the grains of which are larger than chickpeas with a tendency towards white and a nice smell and an oily pulp about which Šayḵ ar-Raʾīs says that it helps against leprosy and melasmata and vitiligo and traces of ulcers and it helps against warts, too, and the salves and decocts applied by bandage are useful against toothache, and another author said it relives scabies and staunches nosebleed."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"spots on the sun or moon etc."},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"amorously attracted"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ka.li.fa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n43096","headword_ar":"كَلَفٌ","root":"klf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A discolouration of the face, by"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that comes upon the face resembling sesame;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[by"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"freckles,"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to present usage:] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dingy redness that comes upon the face."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}